1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
Science has a clearer story about moraines than social media does.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:09,200
Moraines are glacial deposits, formed as glaciers move and reshape the landscape.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:13,600
But did you know they can tell us about past climates?

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:19,600
Different types of moraines, like terminal and lateral, show us how glaciers advanced and retreated.

5
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:27,200
So, next time you see a ridge or mound, think about the history it holds—layers of ice and time.

6
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:30,000
Curious about more wonders of our planet?

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,800
Like and follow for more science stories!
